### =========================================================================
### Learnova - Person 3 (Learner & Payment) API Tests
### Requires REST Client Extension in VS Code
### =========================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_LEARNER_JWT_TOKEN


### =========================================================================
### LEARNER MODULE
### =========================================================================

### 1. Browse Published Courses (Public or Signed-in based on visibility rules)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/published
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 2. Get Course Detail Page (Overview, Progress, Reviews)
@courseIdToView = clt_course_id_here
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseIdToView}}/detail
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 3. Enroll In a Course
POST {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseIdToView}}"
}


### 4. Get My Enrollments (My Courses Page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollments/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 5. Get Course Progress for an Enrollment
@enrollmentId = clt_enrollment_id_here
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollments/{{enrollmentId}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 6. List Course Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseIdToView}}/reviews


### 7. Add Course Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseIdToView}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent course structure and very informative!"
}



### =========================================================================
### PLAYER MODULE
### =========================================================================

### 8. Mark Lesson Started / Completed (and update time spent)
@lessonId = clt_lesson_id_here
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/progress/lesson/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCompleted": true,
  "timeSpentSeconds": 120,
  "enrollmentId": "{{enrollmentId}}"
}


### 9. Load Lesson details for Player
GET {{baseUrl}}/player/{{courseIdToView}}/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 10. Start a New Quiz Attempt
@quizId = clt_quiz_id_here
POST {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/{{quizId}}/attempt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 11. Submit Answer for one Question in an Attempt
@attemptId = clt_attempt_id_here
@questionId = clt_question_id_here
@selectedOptionId = clt_option_id_here
POST {{baseUrl}}/attempts/{{attemptId}}/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "{{questionId}}",
  "selectedOptionId": "{{selectedOptionId}}"
}


### 12. Complete Quiz Attempt (Calculates points + badge)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attempts/{{attemptId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### =========================================================================
### PAYMENT MODULE
### =========================================================================

### 13. Create Razorpay/PayPal Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseIdToView}}"
}


### 14. Verify Webhook Signature -> Sets SUCCESS -> Creates Enrollment
# You will get order_id and payment_id from Razorpay UI testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseIdToView}}",
  "razorpay_order_id": "order_XXXXXX",
  "razorpay_payment_id": "pay_XXXXXX",
  "razorpay_signature": "SIGNATURE_HASH_HERE"
}


### 15. List User's Payment History
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
